    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Kurashi Clan, Level 8+ </p><p>You return to your studies at schools of the Kurashi clan and work to excel in a new field. <br />You gain the following benefits;</p><ul><li><p>Increase your Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma score by +1, to the maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>You gain access to another <strong>School</strong> from your <em><strong>School of Academia</strong></em> feature.</p></li><li><p>Select one <strong>School</strong> from your <em><strong>School of Academia</strong></em> feature. You gain proficiency in the saving throw attributed to your chosen school's attribute. At 16th level, you may select a second school's saving throw to become proficient in.</p></li></ul>",
